  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992740/extras/8a017fde70a9f6098610e55a49631b5d.avif?t=1723225603\" width=616 height=140 /></span><br><br><strong>Towerheart</strong> is a simple sokoban-style puzzle game where you can swap with objects.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992740/extras/2ddf2685c236d430da387216b9f27045.poster.avif?t=1723225603\" width=616 height=104 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992740/extras/2ddf2685c236d430da387216b9f27045.webm?t=1723225603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992740/extras/2ddf2685c236d430da387216b9f27045.mp4?t=1723225603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992740/extras/b559d9f919aa9890a82967fb747bdb51.webp?t=1723225603\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br><br>The Tower is the last hope of a dying world. A mysterious traveler invites the Hero to a giant Tower in the middle of the wasteland to pass its trials. Explore the floors of the Tower, solve its mysteries and meet other travelers on your way. Conquer the Tower and uncover its secrets.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992740/extras/97a471b1136dd77650da591e0688ae9e.webp?t=1723225603\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>80+ Levels<br></li><li>Pixel Art visuals<br></li><li>Animated cutscenes<br></li><li>Secrets</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992740/extras/79b106e66a41da5488e483fc9e0ba2e4.poster.avif?t=1723225603\" width=616 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992740/extras/79b106e66a41da5488e483fc9e0ba2e4.webm?t=1723225603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992740/extras/79b106e66a41da5488e483fc9e0ba2e4.mp4?t=1723225603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
